NAME

    CookLang - Perl Cooklang parser

VERSION

    version 0.11

SYNOPSIS

        my $source = <some Cooklang text>;
        my $recipe = Recipe->new( $source );
        my $ast = $recipe->ast;
        ...

DESCRIPTION

    For the Cooklang syntax, see [Cooklang](https://cooklang.org/).

NAME

    Cooklang - Perl Cooklang parser

AVAILABILITY

    Cooklang is implemented using Object classes as defined in Object::Pad
    which seems to require Perl 5.26

COMMUNITY

    - [Code repository, Wiki and Issue
    Tracker](https://gitlab.com/perl5182717/CookLang) -
    [CPAN](https://metacpan.org/pod/CookLang)

BUGS

    Please report any bugs or feature requests to bug-role-rest-client at
    rt.cpan.org, or through the web interface at
    http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=Cooklang.

